# User Profile Card Generator

A Flask-based web application that generates a stylish user profile card using user input.

## Features

- User-friendly form interface
- Accepts:
  - Name
  - Email
  - Bio
  - Profile Image URL
- Generates dynamic profile card
- Modern responsive UI
- Flask backend integration
- Handles POST requests

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask
- HTML
- CSS

